reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice alternative to swallowing a pill!
reviews.reviewText: I take lots of supplements, and I was seeking a B-12 vitamin to help with energy. I definitely notice a difference when I am taking these consistently. They taste great, and I always save them for last when I am taking my other supplements which I swallow with water. One thing I will note, I would recommend not putting these in any type of medicine box for very long. I would take them straight from the bottle. I have noticed the taste changes if I keep them in my medicine box, and they almost become stale tasting. But straight from the bottle they are great! Overall I would highly recommend trying these and I will definitely repurchase.
